item.description: SoftLayer_Container_Monitoring_Alarm_History Datatype Description The SoftLayer_Container_Monitoring_Alarm_History data type contains information relating to SoftLayer monitoring alarm history. Local accountId Account ID that this alarm belongs to Type: integer agentId ID of the monitoring agent that triggered this alarm Type: integer alarmId Alarm ID Type: string closedDate Time that an alarm was closed. Type: dateTime createDate Time that an alarm was triggered Type: dateTime
